  {
    question: "How often does the DMPX-014 need to be cleaned?",
    answer: "The DMPX-014 is a self-cleaning (automatic discharge) centrifuge — accumulated sludge is ejected automatically every 10–60 minutes depending on the sludge discharge timer setting and the solids loading of the feed. There is no need to stop the machine to clean the bowl. Manual bowl disassembly is only required for annual or bi-annual deep cleaning and inspection."
