    </div>
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-200">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy mb-2">Emulsified Waste Oil with High Water Cut</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-light">Tank bottoms, oilfield slop, and industrial oily water with 20&ndash;60% water content require three-phase centrifugation to break the emulsion and recover usable oil. The DMPX-014 handles feeds with significant water cut that two-phase centrifuges cannot process efficiently.</p>
    </div>
